(firstQuint)A Study to Investigate ICP-022 in Chinese Patients With CLL/ SLL.

 Part I: Safety evaluation -2 regimens of ICP-022 (High and low dose QD) are designed for safety assessment.

 The recommended dose of phase II clinical study will be determined according to the Part I results.

 Part II: Dose expansion -Anti-tumor effects of ICP-022 in Chinese patients with R/R CLL/SLL will be evaluated in approximately 80 subjects.

 The recommended Phase 2 dose will be used in the Part II.

